<h4 class="sidefont">Objectives of Embedded Systems Lab:</h4>
<p class="textfont">
To learn Basic hardware and software concepts in the analysis and design of embedded systems, peripheral interfaces and performance analysis with hands-on design project.

To design embedded computer system hardware

To formulate an embedded computer system design problem including multiple constraints, create a design that satisfies the constraints, implement the design in hardware and software, and measure performance against the design constraints
</p><br>
<h4 class="sidefont">How the lab is embedded into the curriculum:</h4>
<p class="textfont">
    

The lab provides a perfect platform for acquiring basic knowledge on Microcontrollers and Microprocessors. Learning Embedded-C Coding skills can make them programming easily for microcontrollers. With this software and hardware skills one can easily do any mini or major projects.
</p>
